Visualizing Errors
==================

This tutorial covers how to visualize the confidence intervals predicted
from error models.

.. code:: ipython3

    import numpy as np

We start by building and fitting an error model using the training and
validation dataset, respectively.

.. code:: ipython3

    error_model = oce.kNNwRMSD1()
